CONTENT:
Hi again!

Not sure if you saw my emails, but we are collaborating with similar companies to yours, helping them optimize payments and manage sensitive data. 💳

By working with Basis Theory, you will:
- Increase authorization rates by building your own payments orchestration, block, or retry logic;
- securely collect any type of data (card, bank, PII, etc.) from any source and route it to any destination; 
- Increase company margins with lower declines;
- Turn on Account Updater for all cards in the vault, or a subset of cards as you define;
- Securely integrate 3DS and Apple Pay 

Happy to exchange ideas and see if there's an opportunity to work together, or, at least, gain valuable insights from one another
